room_title: Escape room "Bonita Winery Room" by Brainstorm Escape Room Bonita Springs in Fort Myers
room_description: You are on the last guided tour of Bonita Winery before closing its doors for a 2-week vacation. The tour guide leaves you in one of the wine cellars and the door automatically locks behind him. You must find the clues to unlock the door or you will be trapped there until they reopen. You have 60 minutes to solve the clues and escape before the winery closes!
